data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom nearly new home is a perfect blend of luxury and comfort. Boasting a convenient downstairs master bedroom, this home is designed to cater to your every need. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space and an eating area.  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating an ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The outdoor living is not to be missed!  Step outside to your own private oasis - a screened-in pool awaits, promising countless days of relaxation and fun. Imagine hosting gatherings with friends and family in this picturesque setting or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars.  as well as privacy with preserve behind the home.  The charming loft provides additional space for a home office, play area, or cozy retreat. With four generously sized bedroom , there's plenty of room for the whole family to unwind and recharge. But the luxury doesn't end there. This property offers resort-style amenities, ensuring that every day feels like a vacation. Whether it's a refreshing dip in the pool, a game of tennis, or a leisurely stroll through beautifully landscaped grounds, you'll find endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and discover the epitome of modern living in this 4-bedroom paradise with a downstairs master bedroom, loft, screened-in pool, and resort-style amenities. Your dream lifestyle awaits!
